# Exclude anything that doesn't belong in the build context for
# `docker buildx build` at the repo root. Without these exclusions, the
# context tarball balloons to multiple GB (Go module cache alone is ~5GB)
# and every build pays the transfer cost on top of the actual compile.

.git
.go-pkg-cache
.claude
.remember

# Generated binaries — the image build compiles fresh inside the Dockerfile.
# Keep pod2daemon/bin so node-driver-registrar is available for the COPY.
bin
**/bin
!pod2daemon/bin

# Test artifacts.
**/*.test
**/coverage.out
**/coverage.txt
**/report
**/artifacts

# Editor / OS cruft.
.idea
.vscode
**/.DS_Store
